{"tid":432383,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"就出隻Harvest Moon係假既,牧場物語叫做Story of Seasons","createTime":"2017-10-11T12:53:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-11T13:16:01.000Z","uid":6366,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"60d927ff372e1af2f7d88175d5f8560768a3826d","tid":432383,"uid":6366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T12:53:46.000Z","msg":"標題唔夠長,其實2014年前既Harvest Moon係真既<br />\n<br />\nFrom Wiki <br />\n北美版名稱<br />\n在2014年之前，從最初的《牧場物語》到2013年在北美發售的《牧場物語 起源的大地》為止，都是由Natsume的北美分公司作為發行商以「Harvest Moon」之名負責發行，並且Natsume持有「Harvest Moon」的商標權。<br />\n直到2014年，系列的開發商Marvelous宣布<span style=\"color: red;\">將系列北美的發行權交給其在北美的發行分公司XSEED Games發行</span>，並將<span style=\"color: red;\">系列名稱更改為「Story of Seasons」</span>。而之後<span style=\"color: red;\">Natsume宣布將自己製作發行繼續使用「Harvest Moon」</span>的牧場模擬類遊戲，並在2014年E3遊戲展上公布了《牧場物語 失落山谷》。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n假野畫風<br />\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/nintendosoup.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/first-look-at-harvest-moon-light-of-hope-on-nintendo-switch.jpg?resize=1038%2C576&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fnintendosoup.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F08%2Ffirst-look-at-harvest-moon-light-of-hope-on-nintendo-switch.jpg%3Fresize%3D1038%252C576%26ssl%3D1&h=d5e17658&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://thezeroreview.global.ssl.fastly.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/harvestmoon2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthezeroreview.global.ssl.fastly.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2Fharvestmoon2.jpg&h=a564a167&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(3DS)<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.google.com.hk/imgres?imgurl=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.vox-cdn.com%2Fthumbor%2FnC8e8V5D61l4e9v0UBArtIZEocQ%3D%2F0x0%3A400x240%2F1200x800%2Ffilters%3Afocal(168x88%3A232x152)%2Fcdn.vox-cdn.com%2Fuploads%2Fchorus_image%2Fimage%2F54798321%2FHMTLV_Screen__06_.0.jpg&amp;imgrefurl=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.polygon.com%2F2017%2F5%2F16%2F15644988%2Fharvest-moon-light-of-hope-pc-ps4-nintendo-switch&amp;docid=u3WMxtJYNTPR2M&amp;tbnid=SBolQD9PF4xEmM%3A&amp;vet=10ahUKEwja18L0y-jWAhWFwrwKHVFLBzYQMwgnKAMwAw..i&amp;w=1200&amp;h=800&amp;bih=632&amp;biw=1288&amp;q=switch%20LIGHT%20OF%20HOPE&amp;ved=0ahUKEwja18L0y-jWAhWFwrwKHVFLBzYQMwgnKAMwAw&amp;iact=mrc&amp;uact=8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Fimgres%3Fimgurl%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fcdn.vox-cdn.com%252Fthumbor%252FnC8e8V5D61l4e9v0UBArtIZEocQ%253D%252F0x0%253A400x240%252F1200x800%252Ffilters%253Afocal%28168x88%253A232x152%29%252Fcdn.vox-cdn.com%252Fuploads%252Fchorus_image%252Fimage%252F54798321%252FHMTLV_Screen__06_.0.jpg%26imgrefurl%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.polygon.com%252F2017%252F5%252F16%252F15644988%252Fharvest-moon-light-of-hope-pc-ps4-nintendo-switch%26docid%3Du3WMxtJYNTPR2M%26tbnid%3DSBolQD9PF4xEmM%253A%26vet%3D10ahUKEwja18L0y-jWAhWFwrwKHVFLBzYQMwgnKAMwAw..i%26w%3D1200%26h%3D800%26bih%3D632%26biw%3D1288%26q%3Dswitch%2520LIGHT%2520OF%2520HOPE%26ved%3D0ahUKEwja18L0y-jWAhWFwrwKHVFLBzYQMwgnKAMwAw%26iact%3Dmrc%26uact%3D8&h=3287c715&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真野畫風(3DS)<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/60/0001359260.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F60%2F0001359260.JPG&h=a51c80e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://3.pic.pc6.com/thumb/up/2015-11/14473133463064435_600_0.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F3.pic.pc6.com%2Fthumb%2Fup%2F2015-11%2F14473133463064435_600_0.jpg&d=ToG9cpkj6Vi99OCoKNxotp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=e028c613\" target=\"_blank\">http://3.pic.pc6.com/thumb/up/2015-11/14473133463064435_600_0.jpg</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://a3.att.hudong.com/06/69/20300544035811148980699321237_s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fa3.att.hudong.com%2F06%2F69%2F20300544035811148980699321237_s.jpg&h=251a4d34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n簡單黎講,黎緊出係PS4,SWITCH,PC果隻Harvest Moon隻唔係物場牧語間公司出,鍾意牧場物語系列既巴絲記得留意"},{"pid":"66b57a9426eb7d518697b5467822091d7d4eee12","tid":432383,"uid":6366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T12:59:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/QdJNyUHwPGI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQdJNyUHwPGI&d=ToG9cpkj6Vi99OCoKNxotp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=b1d1ef1d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/QdJNyUHwPGI</a><br />\n仲有段片可以比大家睇下<br />\nNatsume Inc好無恥咁講而家係Harvest Moon既20週年<br />\n當中有大家最鍾意既礦石鎮係到<br />\n<br />\n但留意2014既書風完全變晒,因為佢拎住Harvest Moon呢個名,自己開始出game"},{"pid":"5955842b476e3d659ac3bb9e75eada4dc0daaf42","tid":432383,"uid":6366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T13:03:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>標題唔夠長,其實2014年前既Harvest Moon係真既<br />\n<br />\nFrom Wiki <br />\n北美版名稱<br />\n在2014年之前，從最初的《牧場物語》到2013年在北美發售的《牧場物語 起源的大地》為止，都是由Natsume的北美分公司作為發行商以「Harvest Moon」之名負責發行，並且Natsume持有「Harvest Moon」的商標權。<br />\n直到2014年，系列的開發商Marvelous宣布<span style=\"color: red;\">將系列北美的發行權交給其在北美的發行分公司XSEED Games發行</span>，並將<span style=\"color: red;\">系列名稱更改為「Story of Seasons」</span>。而之後<span style=\"color: red;\">Natsume宣布將自己製作發行繼續使用「Harvest Moon」</span>的牧場模擬類遊戲，並在2014年E3遊戲展上公布了《牧場物語 失落山谷》。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n假野畫風<br />\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/nintendosoup.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/first-look-at-harvest-moon-light-of-hope-on-nintendo-switch.jpg?resize=1038,576&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fnintendosoup.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F08%2Ffirst-look-at-harvest-moon-light-of-hope-on-nintendo-switch.jpg%3Fresize%3D1038%2C576%26ssl%3D1&h=1600ae30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n(3DS)<br />\n<img src=\"http://media1.gameinformer.com/imagefeed/screenshots/HarvestMoonTheLostValley/HMTLV%20Screen%20(05).jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia1.gameinformer.com%2Fimagefeed%2Fscreenshots%2FHarvestMoonTheLostValley%2FHMTLV%2520Screen%2520%2805%29.jpg&h=d9080d3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真野畫風(3DS)<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/60/0001359260.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F60%2F0001359260.JPG&h=a51c80e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://3.pic.pc6.com/thumb/up/2015-11/14473133463064435_600_0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F3.pic.pc6.com%2Fthumb%2Fup%2F2015-11%2F14473133463064435_600_0.jpg&h=84d98c84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://a3.att.hudong.com/06/69/20300544035811148980699321237_s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fa3.att.hudong.com%2F06%2F69%2F20300544035811148980699321237_s.jpg&h=251a4d34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n簡單黎講,黎緊出係PS4,SWITCH,PC果隻Harvest Moon隻唔係物場牧語間公司出,鍾意牧場物語系列既巴絲記得留意</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n第二張貼錯左,呢張先係"},{"pid":"21e20ebc89ef025908eec4be7ba49382d45fb06e","tid":432383,"uid":71496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T13:07:15.000Z","msg":"第二張圖係psp黎<br />\n十年前出 當年都有玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d9db1e060ef77ea16496348930d69674b13e1b2","tid":432383,"uid":6366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T13:12:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第二張圖係psp黎<br />\n十年前出 當年都有玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n果張係真野黎<br />\n貼錯左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db879afb55f8b7f881fccd5b8b7e422de34a1d67","tid":432383,"uid":71496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T13:16:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>第二張圖係psp黎<br />\n十年前出 當年都有玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n果張係真野黎<br />\n貼錯左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我知<br />\n未話係psp 好似係蜜糖村<br />\n初中個時玩 咁就十年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}